text: Bounnhang Vorachith (; born 15 August 1937) is a Laotian politician. He was General Secretary of the Lao People's Revolutionary Party and President of Laos from 2016 to 2021. He was Prime Minister from 2001 to 2006 and Vice President of Laos from 2006 to 2016. ==References== Category:1938 births Category:Living people Category:Prime Ministers of Laos Category:Presidents of Laos Category:Vice presidents of Laos
